      "text": [
        "[دخول مكة]\nفإذا أردت دخول مكة فاجهد أن تدخلها على غسل بسكينة ووقار."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "ENTERING MAKKAH\nWhen you intend to enter Mecca, make an effort to enter in a state of ghusl (ritual purification), with tranquility and dignity."
        ]
      }
